{"tid":416110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得覺買macbook大學上堂然後又要裝window好撚反智","createTime":"2017-09-27T13:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T03:10:55.000Z","uid":143400,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a19dcdb366af5d46143c14b67464e04a201000c5","tid":416110,"uid":143400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:46:11.000Z","msg":"講清楚先 唔係話用macbook反智。我而家上堂成日見到有人有人買部萬幾嘅macbook pro然後run唔到professor俾個啲野要搞到裝返window，但明明我一早同佢講左professor話上堂最好要用window機屌你同價位黎講macbook啲spec已經係廢撚到冇朋友，屌你佢都on99"},{"pid":"6bbd265667cf487953eea3073d11aecd79d43696","tid":416110,"uid":15182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:42:04.000Z","msg":"行雙system又點計"},{"pid":"329cbcba2e207f4b9d37e25813f8f92713dfec13","tid":416110,"uid":143400,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T03:10:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行雙system又點計</blockquote><br />\n咁直接用win機好過，手。機黎講ios好用過android好多又唔lag，但labtop黎講佢個os真係唔會好window好多"}]}